<input class="action" type="button" name="show" value="Play" onclick="play_media(<%= @sounds %>,<%= @images %>,<%= @bg_sound %>)"
       />
(If sound fails, try refreshing and clicking Play. Sound buffer can be temperamental.)
<div id="wrapper">
  <div class="slider-wrapper theme-default">
    <div class="ribbon"></div>
    <div id="slider" class="nivoSlider" style="width: 500px !important;height:450px !important; margin: 0 !important;">
      <% @imgs.each do|img| %>
        <% unless img.blank? %>
          <img src="<%= img['src'] %>" alt="" />
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>